    "name": "Spellpowder: Uprising",
    "steam_appid": 1775320,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775320/extras/4b07ee62fa2d081b782246b10b5d2ae2.avif?t=1769809638\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grim news spreads across the Eborean Empire - nobles, those born with the gift of Magia, are vanishing without a trace! Reports from neighboring kingdoms and republics tell of similar disappearances, all unfolding as gunpowder weapons and steam engines are starting to reshape the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whispers speak of the Uprising - a rebellion rising from the common folk, determined to overthrow noble rule at any cost.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With this threat endangering your life, gather a party of skilled companions, uncover the truth behind the disappearances, and stop their plans - before it's too late. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775320/extras/20852ff8b8244a7182d1df9b23981882.poster.avif?t=1769809638\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775320/extras/20852ff8b8244a7182d1df9b23981882.webm?t=1769809638\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775320/extras/20852ff8b8244a7182d1df9b23981882.mp4?t=1769809638\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775320/extras/c7502279a3d823b9176220b667d07b2b.avif?t=1769809638\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight the enemies in a grid based strategy turn based battles in a way you want:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your own character from different fantasy races and backgrounds, be it Noble or Commoner.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use different weapons for different needs - from two-handed mauls to throwable poison bottles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If weapons are not enough, various class skills will help you get an edge.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather experience and level up you and your companions to make them stronger and to unlock new classes to upgrade to.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775320/extras/bb62350968682a936abed85a537f245d.poster.avif?t=1769809638\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775320/extras/bb62350968682a936abed85a537f245d.webm?t=1769809638\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775320/extras/bb62350968682a936abed85a537f245d.mp4?t=1769809638\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775320/extras/aacf572b83cbbcc8d75f98cb84ffa073.avif?t=1769809638\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plan your next moves and prepare for upcoming battles in your own airship:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade airship for various boons in battle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equip and purchase new weapons and upgrade your party members classes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade weapons that you currently have in exchange for some scrap found in battles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run around in circles if you want, airship acts as a hub so your character can move freely</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775320/extras/f44cd4f652557b8d49b695e570610a97.poster.avif?t=1769809638\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775320/extras/f44cd4f652557b8d49b695e570610a97.webm?t=1769809638\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775320/extras/f44cd4f652557b8d49b695e570610a97.mp4?t=1769809638\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775320/extras/95ea6192a34380227b2b0653cf48f287.avif?t=1769809638\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >it's dangerous to go alone, so there will be companions to help you: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equip and upgrade each one as needed</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fighting near them will increase their devotion towards you</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >High devotion will give small buffs for you and companion</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special optional mission for each companion with unique reward</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And tea drinking of course</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775320/extras/1b1979ebc985512f81de2f3f64ccedaa.poster.avif?t=1769809638\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775320/extras/1b1979ebc985512f81de2f3f64ccedaa.webm?t=1769809638\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775320/extras/1b1979ebc985512f81de2f3f64ccedaa.mp4?t=1769809638\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
